## Leyline System

The Living World contains a planetary network of metaphysical energy known as **ley lines**.

Leylines:

- distribute energy throughout the world
- connect naturally occurring nexus points
- interact unpredictably with mortal magic

Ley disruptions are responsible for many supernatural anomalies.

---

## Soul Phenomena

Not all supernatural manifestations involve Arbiters.

Ley interaction may produce several forms of soul interaction:

- heroic soulbound spirits
- failed Arbiter candidates
- ley echoes
- rare Arbiter vessels

Some of these phenomena are linked to the experiments of **Loughan Begarrow**, a scholar studying soul-ley interactions.

